  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Global Media Fellowship to Promote Untold Stories</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will provide emerging filmmakers and journalists from developing countries with access to media training and a Fellowship, which gives them a production grant, mentors and training to complete their reporting. We know the vital role of a free and plural media in opening our eyes to diversity of the world around us. We give new talent who may be looking for their first director role or their first solo investigation the backing to tell under-reported stories.</narrative>
